;; 1. What does [collatz-len 3 0] give? Trace it by hand:
;;    3 → 10 → 5 → 16 → 8 → 4 → 2 → 1 (7 steps)
;; 2. Write an `is-even?` function: [int-eq [int-mod n 2] 0]
;; 3. Compute [fact 7]. What's 7!?
